{"tid":758740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去年916宗自殺亡　青少年增5成最細僅7歲","createTime":"2018-07-28T04:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T04:43:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b30660f3b878e2e75084e68da4829b98dd525c6","tid":758740,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180728/photo/bkn-20180728114201064-0728_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180728120131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180728%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180728114201064-0728_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180728120131&h=b780c3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自殺問題備受社會關注，香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會根據死因裁判庭統計，2017年共有916宗自殺死亡個案，較2016年下跌38宗，但當中36宗為19歲或以下的青少年，比2016年上升50%，最低年齡為7歲。機構於2017年處理124宗青少年具自殺危機的個案，最多個案與家庭問題有關(24%)，其次為學業問題(20%)。 <br />\n<br />\n至於長者自殺問題，70歲或以上的長者為2017年自殺人士中，佔數最多的群組(24%)。自殺危機處理中心主任何永雄表示，長者自殺的原因主要與喪偶及子女去世有關。總幹事曾展國則指，很多長者怕造成他人負擔而不求助，有些則不知道有何求助途徑。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180728/bkn-20180728114201064-0728_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180728%2Fbkn-20180728114201064-0728_00822_001.html&d=%2FF6NHTlpM1XLyYUFGzugF8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=620e06f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180728/bkn-20180728114201064-0728_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4141241a58eeb6f409d2f8d23c27c5581ce289cb","tid":758740,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6d533cba168a1e88b37f6a27df64940a237bf60","tid":758740,"uid":116896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"差唔多一日就有3個人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46